
1. Installation
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

To install hlfl, do :

./configure
make
make install


Everything will be stored under /usr/local. If you want hlfl to be installed
somewhere else, then do :

	./configure --prefix=/path/where/you/want/hlfl/to/live


Some files will be stored in /usr/local/share/hlfl. If you want them
to be stored at some other place, then do :

	./configure --datadir=/path/to/the/dir/you/want

2. Usage
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

	Please read doc/syntax.txt and/or 'man hlfl'


